Considering the Target Audience and Information about myself, give me a topic outline for the heading "Understanding Latent Conditions in Construction: A Homeowner's Guide". The article should appeal to the Target Audience who receive a variation for latent conditions where the homeowner is building a new build or renovation of the residential home. There should be analysis of latent conditions commonly found in new builds vs renovations.

I also want you to maintain a word count of 1,300 words
